column5: Hey everyone.  Short notice but our club is holding our second annual "Kempenfelt Open" tomorrow.  Launch is at the marina in downtown Barrie, blastoff is at 7:30am, weigh-in is at 3:00pm.  $120.00 per team plus an optional $20.00 big fish pool.  It is a 4 fish limit, and despite the name of the event, it is not restricted to the bay, the entire lake is open .  Should be a good payout.  Hope to see a few of you out there!  More info can be found at www.barriebassmasters.org
Sounds like a good time Steve. I hope you get a good turnout. Looking forward to seeing what the lady coughs up.
Thanks Steve maybe i will see the weigh in.

Check out the link for full results, it was a great day but tough bite for most.  http://www.timeonthewater.org/BBMsimcoe_open_2008.html
